ackground-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;Lệnh 1 (Fetch):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; &quot;Đi hỏi&quot; server xem có gì mới nhất không và tải về bản nháp.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Yjhzub&quot; data-sfc-root=&quot;c&quot; data-sfc-cb=&quot;&quot; data-complete=&quot;true&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Yjhzub&quot; data-sfc-root=&quot;c&quot; data-sfc-cb=&quot;&quot; data-complete=&quot;true&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;Lệnh 2 (Reset --hard):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; &quot;Đập đi xây lại&quot; thư mục cục bộ theo đúng bản nháp vừa tải về.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&