        <mxCell id="czMzne_ZfhmWIMXkXQRc-57" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;main.py&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(31, 35, 40); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;API này là endpoint FastAPI&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; tab-size: 4; white-space: break-spaces; background-color: rgba(129, 139, 152, 0.12); border-radius: 6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; color: rgb(31, 35, 40);&quot;&gt;POST /run-embulk&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(31, 35, 40); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;dùng để: nhận request JSON → chọn “template” YAML embulk từ&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; tab-size: 4; white-space: break-spaces; background-color: rgba(129, 139, 152, 0.12); border-radius: 6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; color: rgb(31, 35, 40);&quot;&gt;yaml_data_dict&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(31, 35, 40); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;→ render thành config file tạm → (tuỳ mode) xoá dữ liệu bảng đích → chạy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; tab-size: 4; white-space: break-spaces; background-color: rgba(129, 139, 152, 0.12); border-radius: 6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; color: rgb(31, 35, 40);&quot;&gt;embulk run &amp;lt;config&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(31, 35, 40); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;→ stream log stdout/stderr → release lock.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
